1. Error-handling middleware + 404 handler (prevents stack-trace leaks)
2. `helmet` + disable `x-powered-by`
3. Rate limiting
4. AuthN on `/users` before it holds real data
5. Validation layer (`zod`/`joi`) baked in before you add input routes
6. Graceful shutdown + `PORT` via env
7. Explicit CORS
8. Structured request logging with redaction

